<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activation link - NextLMS</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222;
        }
        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .email-footer {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to NextLMS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %></p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with NextLMS, To activate your account,
            please use the following activation code: 
        </p>
        <h2> <%= activationCode %> </h2>
        <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within 1 hour</p>
        <p>If you did not register your account with NextLMS, please ignore this email</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
            If you have any questions,
            please don't hesitate to contact us at 
            <a href="mailto:support@nextlms.com">support@nextlms.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
   </div> 
</body>
</html>